reviews.title: Not as good as other banks
reviews.comment: They need to add the function where you can deposit checks by taking pictures with your camera.  That would earn a 5 star rating.
reviews.author: Matt Kunstman

reviews.title: Could be better, needs to play catchup, fast.
reviews.comment: Password and security question on every login... Takes too long to quickly check your account on the go. Simpler to just use the browser at home. Very basic app... Needs to play some major catch up since most banks have had apps for years, but it is a decent start.
reviews.author: Matthew Pool

reviews.title: Annoying Log in.
reviews.comment: First impression it looks nice and has the funcionality you would expect from this kind of app. I only gave it 3 stars because you made me scroll through a terms of service when I first logged in. I already bank with you, I don\'t need to see it again. Second don\'t make me answer a security question every time I log in. Put in a \"remember this device\" option.
reviews.author: Ryan Lynn

reviews.title: APP
reviews.comment: Not going to pay the 75 cent fee for each check I want to deposit. Goodbye capfed mobile app.
reviews.author: Kellie N

reviews.title: Dumb
reviews.comment: Won\'t let me log in, so it\'s pretty pointless
reviews.author: Mac Brooks

reviews.title: Doesn\'t work on tablet
reviews.comment: On my galaxy 10 it won\'t bring up the keyboard to answer the security question.
reviews.author: Brad Minion

reviews.title: Can\'t login
reviews.comment: Set it up on my phone with the activation and such but keeps telling me I can\'t log in.
reviews.author: Robert Haney

reviews.comment: Awesome features and easy to use.
reviews.author: Ryan Sinovic

reviews.title: Fee for mobile deposit!
reviews.comment: Come on Cap Fed!? What is the point of a mobile app if there is a fee for mobile deposit? I\'ll use a different bank that doesn\'t charge a fee.
reviews.author: Austin Delimont

reviews.title: Security answer
reviews.comment: You shouldn\'t have to enter your security answer every time you login from the same device. It is very annoying.  Also, once the deposit checks functionality begins to work...it\'s going to charge me $0.75 every time I decide to use it?? Bank of America is free.
reviews.author: Edward Patterson

reviews.title: Good app
reviews.comment: Check deposit through the app would be very nice to have.
reviews.author: Devang M

reviews.title: Great bank, great app
reviews.comment: This is precisely what I wanted to make my customer experience complete. Good looking app, quick transitions, and everything I need in banking at my fingertips.
reviews.author: Darren Brubaker

reviews.title: Port
reviews.comment: When you ported the app, you couldn\'t bother to update your description to modify the bit about using an iPhone.
reviews.author: Anthony Hauk
